name: 💜 Happy Pride Month 💜
description: 🌈❤️🧡💛💚💙💜 Although Beca's a very angry cat, even she knows that love is all that matters by the end of the day. So I hope you all love each other a lot and live a very happy life without prejudice and hate. Let's just spread love, always. This is a happy pride month message from Beca. A big meow to you all. P.S: this is a special bonus edition 🌈❤️🧡💛💚💙💜
